  {name: "2010 Holiday Ale", description: "To celebrate the 2010 holidays, we made a special batch of our Belgian Style Pale Ale. The first batch of Belgian Style Pale bottled from our new seven barrel brewhouse! By special request, a few bottles were our Indulgence.\n\nAll bottles were sold with a customized To and From label. This example is just one way the bottles were labeled. We even had a couple of bottles leave from Santa, the best wife ever and our most handsome fan!", abv: nil, img: nil, avg_score: nil, user_id: nil, brewery_id: 9131, availability_id: nil, type_id: 70, brewery_db_id: "TaRTgY"},
